&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The Financial Services Representative (FSR) role is responsible for the consistent oversight, execution and accuracy of the financial status from registration through post-travel reconciliation for approximately 150 to 250 assigned travel group Program Leaders (PL) and associated Participants&#39; Responsible Parties (RP). The FSR has a strong working knowledge across WorldStrides products, policies, workflows, and platforms and performs across these with a quantifiable bias towards productivity, efficiency, and quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
