&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Leveraging strong relationship management skills across internal and external stakeholders, the FSR&#39;s success lies in their ability to efficiently manage the groups&#39; financial dynamics through the timely communications with the PL, the proper distribution of school monies and the collection of all monies due from the groups&#39; traveling School/PAX while maintaining a PL Post Trip Survey average rating of over 9 on a 10 point scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
